{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126104321910378496258497.jpeg/H-XGqnLmJWuHlJGoy0mZqN8ZCU9CMHKkbei1LG3otSw\" alt=\"陳楨怡到峇里島度假。（ig@celina_harto）\"><figcaption>陳楨怡到峇里島度假。（ig@celina_harto）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126104335286538240081365.jpeg/UOiU5ZF8ZP2P2lxT7GS4Z8n_ne64IQ_u8HKZjfBymY0\" alt=\"大騷身材。（ig@celina_harto）\"><figcaption>大騷身材。（ig@celina_harto）</figcaption></figure><p>豹紋墨鏡裝扮被指撞樣Jennie</p><p>向來身材高挑的陳楨怡，在旅途中換上多套火辣穿搭，其中一套豹紋Tube Top配搭白色短裙最為吸睛。有網民留言大讚其氣質與神態與BLACKPINK成員Jennie極為相似，直呼：「以為見到Jennie！」</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126104333147312128678235.jpeg/pqWgqFbbuH9G-jc-J-4m522Ea0ZLkyuyPclXvD3JV7w\" alt=\"陳楨怡被讚神似Jennie。（ig@celina_harto）\"><figcaption>陳楨怡被讚神似Jennie。（ig@celina_harto）</figcaption></figure><p>陳楨怡大騷Model級身材</p><p>陳楨怡不僅大曬「黃蜂腰」與逆天長腿，更驚現勤力健身的成果，腹部隱約露出的腹肌線條極度搶FO。除了正面照震撼眼球，陳楨怡亦分享了多張背影及側身照，完美展現出其標誌性的肩頸線條和小蠻腰。網民紛紛留言大讚其身材比例簡直是名模級數，驚嘆「身材好到極致」、「靚到絕」、「簡直是名模比例」。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126104326096293888364728.jpeg/tk0YbFzNPYI8vrYL2N1RKGBjA8rJnd1OrLcuxKy3LsQ\" alt=\"腹肌極搶Fo。（ig@celina_harto）\"><figcaption>腹肌極搶Fo。（ig@celina_harto）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126104330701901824905726.jpeg/kM-L7CMsV4o9bqVZzu89LD4x1oGTA8_aP0XiNz9F4jc\" alt=\"九頭身身材！（ig@celina_harto）\"><figcaption>九頭身身材！（ig@celina_harto）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126104328516538368178936.jpeg/2JgvieadbQlb8y-h0npRh537hpUDaHq_DUNyjA1Dcow\" alt=\"大騷小蠻腰。（ig@celina_harto）\"><figcaption>大騷小蠻腰。（ig@celina_harto）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T05:51:47.933322+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":428,"images":6,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}